The National Stock Exchange of India
Ltd. added four companies including  Coal India Ltd. (COAL)  to its list
of futures and options, the bourse said in a statement.  Delta Corp Ltd. (DELTA) ,  Dhanlaxmi Bank Ltd. (DHLBK)  and Gujarat
Fluorochemicals Ltd. are the other additions that take effect
Aug. 5, the exchange said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
